sequenceDiagram
    autonumber

    participant User as User / Data Scientist
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant MutWH as Mutating Webhook<br/>9443/TCP HTTPS
    participant ValWH as Validating Webhook<br/>9443/TCP HTTPS
    participant AuthCtrl as Authentication Controller
    participant mTLSCtrl as mTLS Controller
    participant NPCtrl as NetworkPolicy Controller
    participant RCCtrl as RayCluster Controller
    participant Gateway as Platform Gateway<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant KRBP as kube-rbac-proxy<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS
    participant RayHead as Ray Head Pod<br/>8265/TCP HTTP
    participant CertMgr as cert-manager<br/>443/TCP HTTPS

    rect rgb(230, 245, 255)
        Note over User,CertMgr: Flow 1: RayCluster Provisioning (RHOAI/OpenShift)
        User->>K8sAPI: POST RayCluster CR<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
        K8sAPI->>MutWH: Mutate RayCluster<br/>TLS / API server mTLS
        Note right of MutWH: Sets enable-secure-trusted-network=true<br/>Forces enableIngress=false
        MutWH-->>K8sAPI: Mutated CR
        K8sAPI->>ValWH: Validate RayCluster<br/>TLS / API server mTLS
        Note right of ValWH: Validates DNS name format<br/>Checks unique worker groups
        ValWH-->>K8sAPI: Admitted

        K8sAPI-->>AuthCtrl: Watch: RayCluster created
        AuthCtrl->>K8sAPI: Create HTTPRoute, ReferenceGrant,<br/>ServiceAccount, ConfigMap<br/>HTTPS / SA Token
        AuthCtrl->>K8sAPI: Set condition: AuthenticationReady=True

        K8sAPI-->>mTLSCtrl: Watch: RayCluster created
        mTLSCtrl->>CertMgr: Create Issuer + Certificate CRs<br/>HTTPS / SA Token
        CertMgr-->>mTLSCtrl: TLS secrets provisioned<br/>(head + worker + CA)

        K8sAPI-->>NPCtrl: Watch: RayCluster created
        NPCtrl->>K8sAPI: Create NetworkPolicy<br/>HTTPS / SA Token

        K8sAPI-->>RCCtrl: Watch: RayCluster created
        Note right of RCCtrl: Waits for AuthenticationReady condition
        RCCtrl->>K8sAPI: Create Head Pod + Services<br/>HTTPS / SA Token
        RCCtrl->>K8sAPI: Create Worker Pods<br/>HTTPS / SA Token
    end

    rect rgb(255, 243, 224)
        Note over User,CertMgr: Flow 2: RayJob Execution
        User->>K8sAPI: POST RayJob CR<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
        Note right of K8sAPI: RayJob Controller creates<br/>RayCluster (if needed)
        K8sAPI-->>RCCtrl: Triggers cluster provisioning
        K8sAPI->>K8sAPI: Create Submitter Job/Pod
        K8sAPI->>RayHead: Submit Ray job<br/>HTTP/8265 (in-cluster)
        RayHead-->>K8sAPI: Job ID
        loop Poll job status
            K8sAPI->>RayHead: GET job status<br/>HTTP/8265
            RayHead-->>K8sAPI: Status
        end
    end

    rect rgb(232, 245, 233)
        Note over User,CertMgr: Flow 3: User Access to Ray Dashboard (RHOAI Gateway API)
        User->>Gateway: GET /ray/{ns}/{cluster}<br/>HTTPS/443 / OIDC Token
        Gateway->>KRBP: Forward via HTTPRoute<br/>HTTPS/8443 / TLS
        Note right of KRBP: SubjectAccessReview<br/>on Service GET
        KRBP->>K8sAPI: SubjectAccessReview<br/>HTTPS/443 / SA Token
        K8sAPI-->>KRBP: Allowed
        KRBP->>RayHead: Proxy to dashboard<br/>HTTP/8265 (localhost)
        RayHead-->>KRBP: Dashboard HTML/API response
        KRBP-->>Gateway: Response
        Gateway-->>User: Dashboard content
    end
